#### [NEW] [firearms.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/tts_niche_rules/firearms.txt)

Pattern-based rules cho niche súng đạn:
- Caliber notation: `.30-30` → `thirty thirty`, `5.56` → `five five six`
- Model codes: `AR-15` → `a r fifteen`, `AK-47` → `a k forty seven`
- Technical terms: `M-LOK` → `m lok`, `MSRP` → `m s r p`
- Brand combos: `S&W` → `s and w`

