#### [NEW] [history.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/tts_niche_rules/history.txt)

Pattern-based rules cho niche lịch sử:
- Dynasty/era names: giữ nguyên phát âm gốc
- Ancient dates: `1200 BC` → `twelve hundred b c`
- Historical titles: `Emperor` / `King` + Roman numerals
- Geographic names: cổ đại vs hiện đại

