### Core Module

#### [MODIFY] [tts_cleanup.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/tts_cleanup.py)

**Thêm 3 hàm mới:**

1. `detect_niche(text, api_client, log_callback)` → `{"niche", "confidence", "reasoning"}`
   - Dùng Flash model, gửi ~1500 ký tự đầu
   - Load prompt `system_tts_detect_niche.txt`

2. `load_niche_rules(niche)` → `str`
   - Đọc file `prompts/tts_niche_rules/{niche}.txt` (e.g. `firearms.txt`, `history.txt`)
   - Trả về `""` nếu niche = `general` hoặc file không tồn tại

3. `export_uncertain_csv(data, path)` → `str`
   - Ghi CSV: `Script | Term | Context | Suggested | Confidence`
   - Cùng pattern locked-file retry như [export_acronym_csv](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/tts_cleanup.py#176-210)

**Sửa [cleanup_for_tts()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/tts_cleanup.py#58-117):**
- Thêm param `niche_rules: str = ""`
- Inject niche_rules vào cuối system prompt
- Parse thêm section `---UNCERTAIN---` từ response
- Return mới: [(cleaned_text, acronyms, uncertain_terms)](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/tts_tab.py#495-702)

